        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "A five-minute tapping practice from Day 32 of the MONEY program. The session works with the tendency to put income in a box: only from clients, only from employment, only from work you can explain. The script opens the box.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "New to tapping? Read ",
